flowchart TD
    A[User visits app] --> B{Has an account?}

    B -->|No| C[Register]
    C --> D[Verification email sent]
    D --> E[Click verify link]
    E --> F[Dashboard]

    B -->|Yes| G[Login]
    G --> H{Email verified?}

    H -->|No| I[403 - email not verified]
    I --> J[Resend verification email]
    J --> E

    H -->|Yes| F

    G --> K[Forgot password?]
    K --> L[Enter email]
    L --> M[Reset email sent]
    M --> N[Click reset link]
    N --> O[Set new password]
    O -->|auto-login| F
